item.atr_query:
select dem_supplier.dem_spr_contact_email
from dem_supplier 
inner join dem_supply on dem_supplier.row_id = dem_sup_spr_id
inner join dem_sup_ord on dem_supply.row_id = dem_supord_sup_id
where dem_sup_ord.dem_supord_ord_id = [row_id]
